{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1e84851749","title":"周士慧“退团申请书”","origin":"《反右派斗争材料汇编》第一集(哈尔滨工业大学校刊编委会编，1957.7.18)。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cc1fd265c8","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":29,"articleId":"1e84851749"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"628e6190ec","name":"哈尔滨工业大学"},{"id":"f751cbb4cd","name":"周士慧"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e18898afba","type":"title","text":"周士慧“退团申请书”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1e84851749"},{"id":"b3d9da85ba","type":"authors","text":"哈尔滨工业大学周士慧","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1e84851749"},{"id":"e638a73588","type":"subtitle","text":"[周士慧：哈尔滨工业大学土木工程系135班学生]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1e84851749"},{"id":"6d31cb7ca8","type":"appellation","text":"135班共青团支部：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1e84851749"},{"id":"bd1512c96d","type":"paragraph","text":"我经过考虑后，提出申请退团，下面简单谈一谈理由。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1e84851749"},{"id":"90cc6fa626","type":"paragraph","text":"首先，根据我的经验，离开团组织是有利的，至少是无害的，团的力量从没有使我走向正确的地方，却相反地推近死亡边缘。（我知道，你们是不会同意这结论的）。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1e84851749"},{"id":"dc11119d84","type":"paragraph","text":"其次，我不愿意和一些伪善人在一起。我不要侮辱。人生活应当平等。我的生活自己支配吧，这样，别人尽可以伪善，不平等、侮辱，我的行动将是自由的。（我不在妨碍别人自由）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1e84851749"},{"id":"56dbfb5955","type":"paragraph","text":"以上就是主要两点理由。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1e84851749"},{"id":"aa49b0eb2d","type":"paragraph","text":"我觉得我一年中生活还不如挨国民党打骂好（在中学有这事），死比活着快活三倍。自然，活着好。由于无知幻想，以前会几度想死。应当活着，让现实代替幻想。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1e84851749"},{"id":"59befbe2ae","type":"paragraph","text":"我丝毫不相信  人之流，如×××等，能在社会中比别人劳动多些；我也不相信他们在极端的情况下（如被敌人拷打），能比别人晚些喊叫。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1e84851749"},{"id":"faefee43d2","type":"paragraph","text":"“善良”的人们，你们永远是“温暖、关心、热情、友谊”的“谢谢”你们。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1e84851749"},{"id":"cf05d807e6","type":"paragraph","text":"快点离开你们吧！窒息、在荒山中饿死也比这里强。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1e84851749"},{"id":"82dec896fd","type":"paragraph","text":"（应当声明，多数同志是友好的，请他们原谅，因为我没接受他们的关心）。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1e84851749"},{"id":"1a585f9ae0","type":"paragraph","text":"处分，甚至开除是整个团组织的事情。我不参加意见。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1e84851749"},{"id":"e496abbf89","type":"paragraph","text":"我不认为这件事是我的大事。我把它看成一阵小旋风迷了眼睛，擦一擦好了再走。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1e84851749"},{"id":"9a3eac878e","type":"paragraph","text":"希望处理","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1e84851749"},{"id":"a35d51d7b0","type":"paragraph","text":" 周士慧57.5.29","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1e84851749"}],"page":{"id":"00cd085860","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1e84851749","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}